的门票将于本周五（2 月 16 日）上午 10 点（格林威治标准时间）开始全面发售 - <a href="https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/pretenders-tickets/artist/821283?irgwc=1&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=2862475&amp;awtrc=&amp;clickId=wwEzBLW-RxyPWNIXqSXj8x-BUkH13413iX3SU00&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;ircid=7559" target="_blank" rel="noopener">您可以在这里购买</a>。</p><p>去年夏天， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-pretenders-dave-grohl-johnny-marr-paul-mccartney-glastonbury-3460389">海德和他的同事们。在 2023 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节的公园舞台上表演</a>，前<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-smiths">史密斯乐队</a>吉他手<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/johnny-marr">约翰尼·马尔</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/foo-fighters">喷火战机</a>主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dave-grohl">戴夫·格罗尔</a>也加入了演出。</p><p>该乐队还在 2023 年伦敦<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/british-summer-time-bst-festival">BST 海德公园</a>为<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/guns-n-roses">Guns N&#39; Roses</a>开场，随后出现在莱斯特的 BBC Radio 2 In The Park 节目中。</p><p>今年夏天， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/foo-fighters-announce-2024-everything-or-nothing-us-stadium-tour-buy-tickets-3507831">伪装者乐队将在 Foo Fighters 的“Everything Or Nothing”美国巡演的选定日期为他们开场</a>，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/johnny-marr-suede-the-pretenders-among-50-new-names-for-isle-of-wight-2024-line-up-3582590">计划在 2024 年怀特岛音乐节上演出</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-pretenders-reschedule-uk-tour-due-to-injury-and-add-more-dates-for-october-2024-buy-tickets-3586800">《伪装者》因受伤重新安排英国巡演并增加 2024 年 10 月的更多日期的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
